Product name: Flowers, world postage stamps | modern  vintage random floral mixed used stamps | crafting, collage, upcycling, decoupage, collecting
Description:
Packet of 20 or 40 Used World Postage Stamps
Flower / Floral Theme Mix, including vintage & more recent
You will receive a random selection of used stamps, all featuring some form of flowers, blossoms, petals or floral arrangement.  Packets may or may not include the exact stamps shown (picture is a representative sampling of my currently available selection but this will be added to regularly).  I will avoid duplicates in any single packet, but there will be duplication if multiple packets purchased at one time.  
Stamps are mostly pre-1996 although there may be one or two more recent, and one or two much older than others. The mix you receive will be randomly selected from those available, but I will try to include a range of different countries.  
Stamps are in good condition, most are used & postmarked although there may be one or two mint unused.  Great for adding an authentic international travel flavour to your upcycled craft projects, greeting cards, scrapbooking etc.  All stamps in each packet are off paper, ready to use/craft (not valid for use as actual postage!)
* * * * *
I use stamps regularly in my own artwork (see my shop: 
http://tanglecrafts.etsy.com
 ).  These packets are made up from the excess which do not fit my own projects - a continual process of sorting & filtering, which means new stamps are frequently added into the mix.  Just a way to keep these otherwise unloved stamps in circulation! 
Please: see my other listings for more themed & mixed used postage stamp packets:
https://www.etsy.com/uk/shop/TangleCrafts?section_id=5914283

Product name: Hairpin Legs - 3 Rod with Round Bottoms
Description:
Hairpin Legs - 3 Rod Style with Round Flat Bottoms and Felt Padding
Listing is for 1 leg
These hairpin legs feature a 3 rod design for extra stability and have a cool unique look.  The base plate is a 4" L made from 1/8" thick steel plate and the legs are solid 3/8" steel rod.  There are 3 mounting 1/4" mounting holes.
At the bottom we weld a 1" round steel foot and attach felt padding. The felt foot saves your hardwood floors and also gives a more comfortable and planted feel to tables/desks - unlike the hard point of standard hairpins.  Our welds are beautiful and it gives the whole leg a seamless blacksmithed look. 
All of our legs come fully finished and clearcoated - Ready to attach.  We use natural steel patina techniques, no spray paint here.  Finishes include:
 -Burnished Gray - A dark marbled gun metal gray; a more rustic/industrial look.  
 -Blackened Patina - Overall black marbled with hints of auburn and brown.  
 
 -Brushed Steel - A bright polished finish, similar to stainless steel. 
All are topped with a durable crystal clear coat.  Mounting screws included
You put effort into you table top, finish it off with some beautiful metal work!
Any questions, feel free to call
Thanks,
Lou
